summary: In this post Taylor is wearing 4 rings...as well as being a fashion accessory rings represent infinity and eternity, suggesting...
body:
Theory: Opals and Rings

In this post Taylor is wearing 4 rings…as well as being a fashion accessory rings represent infinity and eternity, suggesting Taylor’s state of mind right know: happy and fulfilled, which of course is all we could want for her. Now, 2 of these rings are Opal, which has its own symbolism that I think relates to Taylor A LOT and could allude to what TS7 songs might be about.

1) opal is the birthstone for October; possible album release month!!

2) opal had a bad rep for a while because of false stories that were published - this could relate to Taylor and the impact that the media had on her…

3) opal is said to enhance confidence and self esteem as encourages you to put out positive emotions. I think this album is going to show the happiness and light Taylor has finally received after all the drama she has had to endure. This is my favourite bit about opals though: “the opal aids in accessing ones true self”. (!!!!!!) This album is going to be th REAL TAYLOR! Not her reputation or an image that has been created to portray to the world. We know that TS7 is the follower Taylor has wanted to release for a while but she had to clear up her name and her reputation first. This confirms that and shows she is finally ready.

4) finally opal is a stone that is associated with love and passion. I think Ts7 is going to be Reputation Part 2 in a way… Reputation was always said to be “for the fans” and it was a treat for those who stood by her. I think Ts7 is going to be like a thank you/love letter to her fans, friends and family for being there for her during the Rep era and all the drama that surrounded that. Also T is SO IN LOVE! We are defo gonna get a bunch of love songs about her and Joe and it’s going to be AMAZING!!

(All the info about opals was from the website jewelsforme.com if you want to check out more about them)

blog.description:
the luminous TayTay ✨ Thai Swiftie                       
💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗💗
I will be in the US from May-Aug 2019 (the only chance I can go to secret session!)

title: Secret Sessions
body:
It’s sad realizing that I will never get to go to the secret sessions because I don’t live in the states…
I just wish we could have a secret session in Thailand too, poor me.

But the good news is that during this school break (May-July), I will be in the states!!!

5 years ago I got a scholarship for an exchange program in the states. I was so happy, thinking that I would get to see Taylor; but I was so unfortunate. I didn’t get to see her because she was touring outside the states at that time. So, I changed my plan and got the ticket for Red Tour in Bangkok. I was scheduled to be back just 2 days before the concert, but then the concert got cancelled because of the military coup in my country. How poor I was!

This year I plan to visit my host family and also hope that I will get to see Taylor!
It’s been 10, almost 11, years now since the release of Fearless, when I become a fan…I keep wishing every day that I get to meet her in person

@taylornation @taylorswift 

please make my wish come true

blog.name: west-coast-taylor
blog.title: 🌻 Always Stay Humble & Kind 🌻
blog.description:
" Someday you'll be just a memory

so make it count" . Hello ! My name is Lisa Cherie Curtis , and this is my blog . Im from Ventura County California . Kids Art Teacher 👩‍🏫🎨

Twitter : cherie_curtis13

My talented friend Followed 12/22/2014.

Born on a December 3rd in 1989. I blog about Tay , music and art . I also am an artist and do portraits of people , and animals, I wish I could afford to go to school, but since I cant I use my talent for good , and donate to help people and animals . Im also a distant relative of Taylors great great great grandfather on Taylors dads side . So does that even count? lol . I have a kitty named catastrophe . I make creative Lyric art and Taylor related things way more than I could ever count. I wore a snake dress and Merch for Reputation to the Grammy’s because I felt like it deserved to be recognized more . May 15th Taylor Surprised me in Vegas and it was beyond amazing and so incredibly sweet of her. I was just super super sick just gotten out of the e.r a day prior . but I never wanted to say or post about it , for people to think I was lying to meet her again. Because that’s not that case. I just want to feel fully there cause I never got to be myself that day. So I really wish one day for a make up day :) . But of course Im super great full ! I love christmas and get overly excited on holidays. I love vintage shopping and black and white things. So obviously I love Reputation. Just be kind to people. You never know what they are going through and just little things you do could make their day. I love the beach, and just sometimes laying on the grass gazing up at the stars and appreciating them , because I mean they are so remarkable if you think about it . And the beach breeze blowing in your hair , 80's music , Shania Twain, The Beach Boys , The eagles . I Love Lucy . Favorite movie is pretty in pink , and A Star is Born .
